        public SimpleLiveLocals​(DirectedBodyGraph<Unit> graph)
        Computes the analysis given a DirectedBodyGraph computed from a method body. It is recommended that a ExceptionalUnitGraph (or similar) be provided for correct results in the case of exceptional control flow.
        Parameters:
        graph - a graph on which to compute the analysis.
        See Also:
        ExceptionalUnitGraph
